{"tid":1431824,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"要求時事台增設文宣區","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T10:41:47.000Z","uid":53349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f77be39c30c48a274f05e05d3b1d6cb7f91aaae7","tid":1431824,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"個人認為依家遊行/示威活動嘅資訊比較混亂，就算定時出一個整合post, 喺時事台都好快沉底。<br />\n<br />\n文宣係涉及創意，但最終目的都係宣傳政治時事活動。<br />\n另外，鑑於時事台活躍程度比政事台高，因此文宣區設於時事台會有效好的宣傳效果。<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為有必要於時事台增設文宣區，俾大家討論關於文宣嘅設計及更新活動資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b53a976394728ca39429301cae52876e3c64475","tid":1431824,"uid":273923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"其實可以所有人只推文宣，其他盡量不推文回覆"},{"pid":"a651c166b13919e066a2589085d253dc6e74b231","tid":1431824,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"文宣停哂手我覺得係大家有少少資訊疲勞<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要宣傳文宣個陣唔該簡單D，直情話俾連登仔聽要做乜野，唔好要人諗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲廢老專用長輩圖---20190808 聲優大招募&amp;FB,TG文宣平台成立啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dzjBoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dzjBoS</a>"},{"pid":"26d69b9503e455739a4187b2935f624872eea52d","tid":1431824,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}